sequenceDiagram
    title <Flow Name> — e.g. User Login Flow

    actor User
    participant SPA as Web App<br/>(React)
    participant API as API<br/>(Node.js)
    participant Auth as Auth Provider
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Cache as Redis

    %% Happy path
    User->>SPA: Submits login form<br/>(email, password)
    SPA->>API: POST /auth/login<br/>{email, password}

    API->>Auth: Verify credentials
    Auth-->>API: Access token + refresh token

    API->>DB: SELECT user WHERE email = ?
    DB-->>API: User record

    API->>Cache: SET session:{userId}<br/>(TTL 24h)
    Cache-->>API: OK

    API-->>SPA: 200 OK<br/>{user, accessToken}
    SPA-->>User: Redirect to dashboard

    %% Error path — invalid credentials
    Note over User,Cache: Alternative: Invalid credentials

    User->>SPA: Submits login form (wrong password)
    SPA->>API: POST /auth/login
    API->>Auth: Verify credentials
    Auth-->>API: 401 Unauthorized
    API-->>SPA: 401 Unauthorized<br/>{error: "invalid_credentials"}
    SPA-->>User: Show error message

    %% Error path — rate limited
    Note over User,Cache: Alternative: Too many attempts

    User->>SPA: Submits login form (5th attempt in 1 min)
    SPA->>API: POST /auth/login
    API->>Cache: INCR rate_limit:{ip}
    Cache-->>API: 6 (over threshold)
    API-->>SPA: 429 Too Many Requests
    SPA-->>User: Show "try again later"
